Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.85,0:00:03.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Previously on Fairy Tail:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.81,0:00:06.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! Jellal's been brought back to life!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.95,0:00:07.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.73,0:00:10.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't bring Wendy back \Nsoon, Erza's in real trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.85,0:00:12.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fast is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.41,0:00:14.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, I'll hold him here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.95,0:00:16.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You hurry to Erza's side!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.94,0:00:17.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fast is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.85,0:00:19.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard ya the first time!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.68,0:00:28.67,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's love and dreams and you it'll become magical.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.67,0:00:35.84,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's cast a smile spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.46,0:00:48.77,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I kind of admired this powerful world,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.77,0:00:53.19,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,chock-full of problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.11,0:00:59.97,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Frozen time has started to move again
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.97,0:01:05.58,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,ever since I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.58,0:01:11.00,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Why were we born? Why do we live?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.00,0:01:16.84,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need any complicated answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.84,0:01:22.78,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Laugh! Cry! Be honest with yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.78,0:01:27.56,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Simple feelings are the most important.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.56,0:01:35.90,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,You can change those tears shed on sad nights into strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.90,0:01:42.53,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's cast a smile spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.34,0:01:55.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Worth Woodsea.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.30,0:02:03.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Deep inside it, there is a single man.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.08,0:02:15.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You okay, Happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.73,0:02:17.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.80,0:02:20.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk. Just rest there a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.80,0:02:22.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Jellal...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.66,0:02:23.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.95,0:02:27.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard! Why the hell is {\i1}he{\i0} here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.11,0:02:30.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:34.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.73,0:02:35.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.63,0:02:38.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.71,0:02:43.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dead Grand Prix!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.67,0:02:50.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu-kun, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.03,0:02:51.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.02,0:02:57.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me. Hibiki, from Blue Pegasus.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.95,0:03:01.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness. I was getting worried \Nafter not being able to contact anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.70,0:03:03.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.70,0:03:08.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not so loud. One of the \Nenemy has very good hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.33,0:03:11.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible he could \Nintercept our conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.48,0:03:14.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm speaking \Ndirectly into your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:18.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how are Wendy-chan and the cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.86,0:03:21.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're here, although she's unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.99,0:03:23.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy's awake, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.87,0:03:25.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.84,0:03:27.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Great job.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.22,0:03:31.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to upload an app directly \Ninto your head that'll guide you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.12,0:03:35.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The cat seems to have used too much magic \Nand taken too much damage for me to connect...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.96,0:03:38.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, hurry back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.29,0:03:41.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. What about an apple?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.00,0:03:42.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.70,0:03:48.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why have you been talking to yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.75,0:03:51.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really get it, but \NI have an apple in my head!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.63,0:03:55.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! I totally know how \Nto get to where Erza is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.46,0:03:57.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like I've known all along!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.41,0:04:00.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any apples in my head!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.34,0:04:02.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, Natsu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.95,0:04:08.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to hurry... There's no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.62,0:04:13.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how did you tell Natsu where we are?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.13,0:04:18.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My magic, Archive, can compress information.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.50,0:04:24.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,By compressing it, people can transfer \Ninformation between each other more quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.84,0:04:27.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never heard of magic like that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.34,0:04:32.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Using magic to convert information into \Ndata is a recent concept, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.48,0:04:35.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.84,0:04:41.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, thank goodness Wendy is safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.95,0:04:44.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait a little longer, Erza.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.70,0:04:45.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.95,0:04:51.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect you until Natsu \Ncomes back. I promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.16,0:05:00.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What are you smiling \Nabout at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.65,0:05:04.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry. I didn't mean to offend you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.90,0:05:14.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Around that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.91,0:05:22.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray is confronting one of \NOracion Seis, codenamed Racer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.22,0:05:26.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've stopped me twice now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.73,0:05:29.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, my name will mean dirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.75,0:05:31.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.69,0:05:36.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I felt like it, it wouldn't be any \Ntrouble to catch up with those brats.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.43,0:05:37.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.48,0:05:40.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I won't feel satisfied \Nuntil you're history.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.84,0:05:43.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have plenty of time \Nto catch up afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.07,0:05:44.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so, buddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.00,0:05:51.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.47,0:05:53.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Slow, slow, slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.24,0:05:55.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! I can't follow him with my eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.36,0:06:01.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you used up your magic \Npower making this ice wall,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.25,0:06:03.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you don't expect me to go easy on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.21,0:06:06.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Say that again, jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.12,0:06:07.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come at me as fast as you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.50,0:06:11.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dead Grand Prix!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.38,0:06:12.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Start your engines!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.65,0:06:22.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of noise is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.74,0:06:29.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic motorcycles!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:36.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell? A ton of magic motorcycles?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.43,0:06:39.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The motor show from hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.18,0:06:43.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.91,0:06:45.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You expect me to ride one of these things?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.98,0:06:49.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,These are machines made \Nto match my own speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.50,0:06:52.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Slowpokes can't handle 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.01,0:06:54.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this just got interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.45,0:07:00.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This bucking bronco is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.12,0:07:02.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Look at him go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:05.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for equipping them with SE plugs!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.57,0:07:07.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The SE Plug:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.14,0:07:13.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In this world, there are many vehicles \Nwhich use magical power as energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.52,0:07:21.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Among them, the magic four-wheelers and \Nmagic motorcycles are equipped with SE Plugs
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.05,0:07:26.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,in order to send magic power from the \Ndriver directly to the internal engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.75,0:07:30.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's definitely tough to make sure I don't \Nlose all my magic power with these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.95,0:07:32.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't got a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.47,0:07:34.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.62,0:07:35.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.95,0:07:38.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're challenging me to a race?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.67,0:07:41.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There ain't no rules, so \Nyou'd better be prepared!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.73,0:07:56.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got some nice style for being a \Ngoody-two-shoes from an official guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.95,0:07:59.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.70,0:08:01.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Make Lance!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.93,0:08:07.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.66,0:08:09.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, it's hard to aim!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.00,0:08:16.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really have the speed to pass me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.22,0:08:18.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,High Side Rush!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.14,0:08:20.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tires?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.35,0:08:24.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.35,0:08:29.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Dead Grand Prix \Nhas just gotten started!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.23,0:08:32.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There! Try getting past this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.91,0:08:43.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, this is nuts!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.59,0:08:45.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, hot stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.70,0:08:59.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't lose! For Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.97,0:09:02.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what the explosion was just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.45,0:09:03.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A newcomer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.80,0:09:04.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.72,0:09:07.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lyon-sama, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.67,0:09:09.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oracion Seis!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.01,0:09:10.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.85,0:09:11.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.13,0:09:14.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect timing! Get on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.74,0:09:15.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.82,0:09:17.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just get on already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.20,0:09:21.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lyon-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.54,0:09:24.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! Stay here on standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.50,0:09:27.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Standby?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.56,0:09:30.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What other choice do I have?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.92,0:09:40.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray, where's Wendy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.20,0:09:43.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. Natsu saved her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.02,0:09:45.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.10,0:09:50.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, can you get him? I can't use \Nmagic well while I'm drivin' this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.36,0:09:53.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you just watch real carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.90,0:09:56.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you how creation magic is done!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.97,0:09:58.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Put your money where your mouth is!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.86,0:09:59.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.60,0:10:03.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pitiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.20,0:10:06.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You still use both hands \Nwhen you use creation magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.33,0:10:10.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lyon... You're using two hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.95,0:10:14.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's how Ul taught us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.70,0:10:19.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Make...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.05,0:10:21.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Eagle!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.87,0:10:24.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You get him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.92,0:10:27.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No... There's no reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.59,0:10:29.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough playing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.35,0:10:32.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Make...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.35,0:10:32.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Make...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.97,0:10:34.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ape!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.52,0:10:36.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hammer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.98,0:10:39.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's some speedy creation \Nmagic you have there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.15,0:10:42.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fast is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.07,0:10:43.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're not there yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.09,0:10:49.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You just can't catch up to my speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.08,0:10:52.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hit him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.75,0:10:55.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm yourself, Gray! He's at 4 o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.60,0:10:59.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you concentrate, you can follow anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.72,0:11:01.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Concentrate, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.47,0:11:02.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.19,0:11:04.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this, Lyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.80,0:11:07.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire on my mark, and don't hold back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.67,0:11:10.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did they strip? And damn, that was fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.10,0:11:13.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did he take off his clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.54,0:11:15.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that also...love?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.45,0:11:28.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now! 50 meters in front!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.33,0:11:29.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.99,0:11:35.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Geyser!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.05,0:11:36.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Snow Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.34,0:11:39.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.41,0:11:41.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's sped up even faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.76,0:11:44.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter? I'm over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.04,0:11:58.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never hit me with those \Nattacks. Not in your entire life...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.80,0:12:01.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can keep up with my speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.13,0:12:05.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's strong... Is this what \NOracion Seis really is?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.80,0:12:10.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I need to get around \Nto finishing you off,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.27,0:12:12.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and bringing back that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.46,0:12:15.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lend me your ear, Gray.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.90,0:12:19.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've found his weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.34,0:12:34.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The results of the investigation are in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.77,0:12:36.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,About Oracion Seis?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.00,0:12:43.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible that Brain was once \Npart of the Bureau of Magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.14,0:12:46.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Bureau of Magic? Then, \Nwhat's his true identity?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.42,0:12:48.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's still under investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.94,0:12:54.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What worries me is the R-system, in \Nother words, the Tower of Heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.88,0:12:57.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This seems to have something to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.04,0:12:59.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got reports indicating that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.97,0:13:02.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a connection to Jellal...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.63,0:13:04.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you mean, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.32,0:13:05.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.59,0:13:08.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.87,0:13:17.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's Brain trying to accomplish with magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.43,0:13:20.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.73,0:13:23.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu and the others are on the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.70,0:13:27.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I'm sure things will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.43,0:13:32.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.00,0:13:36.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be nice if they don't destroy \Nthings any more than necessary, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.80,0:13:39.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's{\i0} what you're worried about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.70,0:13:45.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lyon-sama... What could he be talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.49,0:13:51.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Having a strategy session? How pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.20,0:13:54.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.44,0:13:56.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.17,0:13:57.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.30,0:14:01.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You are no longer needed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.90,0:14:04.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Lyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.01,0:14:05.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.82,0:14:07.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lyon-sama, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.28,0:14:11.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,God damn it! Let me go, Lyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.32,0:14:12.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me this crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.79,0:14:17.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just stay up there and watch, Gray!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.03,0:14:20.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Turning on your friend? That's harsh, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.95,0:14:23.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, don't get me wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.54,0:14:25.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.77,0:14:28.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We just happened to have the same teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.61,0:14:30.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.18,0:14:30.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.14,0:14:33.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But Lyon-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.24,0:14:34.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No complaining!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.93,0:14:37.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lamia Scale will be bagging this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.70,0:14:39.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Sherry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.83,0:14:41.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.95,0:14:47.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That overconfidence isn't \Ngoing to help your chances.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.28,0:14:51.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, your chances were zero \Nto begin with anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.62,0:14:53.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yap-yap-yap, little doggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.37,0:14:57.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Doll Attack, Rock Doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.63,0:15:02.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice power, but it lacks speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.29,0:15:04.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Slow, slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.55,0:15:06.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.92,0:15:10.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case... Wood Doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.56,0:15:14.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't catch me with magic like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.85,0:15:16.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about this, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.70,0:15:18.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.91,0:15:20.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...Psych.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.56,0:15:22.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He slipped out?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.41,0:15:24.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.62,0:15:30.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you, slow in the head?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.84,0:15:34.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.38,0:15:36.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one that's slow in the head!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.00,0:15:40.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your weak point is the \Nweakness of your attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.62,0:15:44.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how fast you are, \Nyou can't seal the deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.20,0:15:48.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Make Hedgehog!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.53,0:15:52.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Close in on me, and you're shish kebab...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.70,0:15:53.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So what'll you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.69,0:15:57.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come at me with that \Nspeed you're so proud of!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.40,0:15:59.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a fool you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.06,0:16:02.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gear Change... Red Zone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.23,0:16:10.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now {\i1}that{\i0} was my top speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.57,0:16:14.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You think I'd be serious at first \Nagainst weaker opponents like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.37,0:16:15.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.65,0:16:16.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.95,0:16:18.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.73,0:16:20.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you think you're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.58,0:16:26.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lyon-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.01,0:16:34.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to that \Nmomentum you had at first?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.41,0:16:42.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you are damn tenacious...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.23,0:16:45.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How far is he going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.57,0:16:55.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Make Eagle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.02,0:16:59.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you understand that you can't hit me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.60,0:17:05.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's wrong? You think \Nyou can stop me with that, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.13,0:17:11.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You said that I don't have any \Nway to seal the deal with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:14.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, since you asked...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.82,0:17:20.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This should do nicely.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.87,0:17:28.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I have the speed, I can get you \Nfirst, before you have a chance to use magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.90,0:17:33.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there's nothing wrong with being \Na bit arrogant when you're young.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.23,0:17:35.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But you were up against the wrong dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.96,0:17:38.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm one of Oracion Seis.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.62,0:17:43.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Six Generals. Six Prayers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.40,0:17:47.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Six Pillars that will never crumble.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.00,0:17:52.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Only death awaits those who rock the pillars.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.10,0:17:54.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.80,0:18:03.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When I saw the birds flying by so fast in the \Nsky, I figured out how your magic really works.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.52,0:18:12.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your magic doesn't increase your own speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.21,0:18:15.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It lowers the speed of your opponents...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.68,0:18:20.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Or more accurately, it slows down\Ntheir sense of time in a certain area.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.84,0:18:24.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, you slow {\i1}me{\i0} down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.51,0:18:30.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And since the magic only \Naffects a certain area,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.65,0:18:33.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,when someone sees you from \Noutside your range...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.54,0:18:40.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They can take away your speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.13,0:18:48.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you had me get \Nso far away from him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.31,0:18:52.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... I see it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.52,0:18:56.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But at that range... \NThere's no way he'll hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.11,0:18:58.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he'll hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.25,0:19:01.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter how far away he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.79,0:19:05.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause there's nothing stronger\Nthan a member of Fairy Tail
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.26,0:19:07.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and the strength of their passion!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.63,0:19:11.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Super Freeze Arrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.55,0:19:18.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.20,0:19:25.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My prayer...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.45,0:19:33.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To be faster than anyone... To be faster...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.92,0:19:50.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it, Lyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.14,0:19:54.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We still got five more of these guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.72,0:19:59.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I actually thought you two \Nwere fighting back there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.15,0:20:02.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd expect nothing less from the older pupil.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.10,0:20:06.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.54,0:20:08.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make fun of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.17,0:20:12.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not over!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.51,0:20:19.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear on the name Oracion Seis, if I \Ngo down in defeat, I'll take you with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.82,0:20:23.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.07,0:20:25.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,An explosive lacrima...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.07,0:20:27.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard... Are you planning on...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.12,0:20:29.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One man, one kill!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.53,0:20:30.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.06,0:20:36.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap... Why do I have to run\Nout of magic power now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.04,0:20:39.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.29,0:20:40.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lyon-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.68,0:20:54.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.80,0:20:58.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The things I do for you, younger pupil...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.33,0:21:16.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.52,0:21:20.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lyon-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.76,0:21:26.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.50,0:21:43.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Racer is... gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.41,0:21:48.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One corner of the Six Generals has broken?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.13,0:21:53.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I underestimated our enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.53,0:21:58.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought I would \Nhave to wake him up...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.75,0:22:00.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Midnight!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.46,0:22:08.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.44,0:22:14.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get rid of every last one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.49,0:22:19.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.84,0:23:59.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I sure wish I could breathe fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.80,0:24:01.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.04,0:24:05.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause I could fry fish, or light \Nup dark places... It's handy!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.61,0:24:07.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't you try eating my flames?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.87,0:24:10.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It might let you use breath attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.45,0:24:13.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cats aren't good with hot food, so I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.98,0:24:16.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.36,0:24:18.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just try eating it, sheesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.11,0:24:20.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's at least a chance, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.06,0:24:22.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're right. Let's see here...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.34,0:24:22.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.58,0:24:24.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,
